{"tid":2208290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"去熟悉既地方會記起前度Ex甚至怕見到佢會心酸","createTime":"2020-09-18T18:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T17:09:23.000Z","uid":215466,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b05adbcaea88849e6840086fa68c72367e0f73be","tid":2208290,"uid":215466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"大家講下一人一個去街見到Ex既故事<br />\n以前成日同佢去既地方：旺角 沙田 鑽石山 元朗 荃灣 大圍 屯門好多......<br />\n宜家一去會諗起好多同佢回憶 <br />\n諗起食飯坐咩位 食咩餸 佢鍾意食咩<br />\n然後個心會痛 好想逃避 連街都唔想去 <br />\n好怕起街見到佢唔知講咩好唔知比咩反應<br />\n但實際上成日左望右望希望見到佢 <br />\n最怕見到佢同佢新歡拍拖 <br />\n有啲野永遠都放唔低 個心一直痛<br />\n最愛那一個 一般沒有結果～"},{"pid":"1bfee09f9cd7226d018782065e11acc41559ff26","tid":2208290,"uid":134103,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:56:00.000Z","msg":"逃生出口的一線光<br />\n流光了眼淚便能看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e49d4440aac85056a44a9f8a2ad4ab0713a032","tid":2208290,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15efb4fc159db05833345342dfa564b20ebeaf07","tid":2208290,"uid":215466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bfee09f9cd7226d018782065e11acc41559ff26","tid":2208290,"uid":134103,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:56:00.000Z","msg":"逃生出口的一線光<br />\n流光了眼淚便能看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T19:06:10.000Z","msg":"有咩故事聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b383dfeaeb7fb2dd19b11e73b7d6fdec8b34be9a","tid":2208290,"uid":139117,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"未放低既時候連飲水都記起佢<br />\n放低既時候就算見到佢都冇反應"},{"pid":"1fa5d649a760a7c4e6f66cd6acd6